---
title: Ginger-Lime Salmon with Wonton Noodle Salad
description: Foil-packets are full of flaky and ginger-lime scented salmon. Served with tender-crisp broccoli and a tasty wonton noodles salad, dinner tonight is impressive and simple to create!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-parfume-au-gingembre-et-a-la-lime-5fbaeba1.jpg
